dcterms:description: A character image dataset containing 1623 hand-written characters from 50 alphabets. Each character contains 20 gray images drawn by different writers. The 1200 characters with rotations (4800 classes) are for training, 100 characters (400 classes) for validation and 323 characters (1292 classes) for testing.
